MSYS Requirements

http://www.mingw.org/download.shtml
Install MSYS
Install msysDTK
Install bash for MSYS
Install wget for MSYS ??
Install date from coreutils for MSYS

http://www.info-zip.org/
Install zip and unzip to tools/zip

Cygwin Requirements

Install basic cygwin plus:
  patchutils
  make (3.80 required)
  perl
  zip
  unzip
  cvs
  
Install quilt for patch management functions
